    "body" : "<p>You can use this to get weekday from the date</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<pre><code>    Calendar currentDate = Calendar.getInstance(); //or your specified date.\n    int weekDay = currentDate.get(Calendar.DAY_OF_WEEK);\n</code></pre>\n</blockquote>\n"
